data.description: Spacious 4BD/3BTH, 2,381 sq.ft. home in the Ashton Park gated subdivision conveniently located in the HWY 211, Potranco Road and Loop 1604 area.  This beautiful home features an open floor plan, island kitchen w/ a huge walk-in pantry and gas cooking, granite throughout, and a separate office that could also be used as a work out area or game room.  Split floor plan with bathrooms conveniently located just off of the 2nd and 3rd bedrooms while the primary suite includes plenty of room in the walk-in closet, double vanity and an oversized walk-in shower.  Outside amenities include covered back patio and front and back sprinkler system. Motivated Seller!
